<p>You can configured the Server Preferred Time Zone by adjusting the PreferredGreenwichMeantimeOffset setting in Web.config or user.config</p>
<p>&lt;add key="PreferredGreenwichMeantimeOffset" value="-5.00" /&gt;</p>
<p>All times are stored as UTC (Universal Time Code also known as Greenwich Mean Time or GMT). Time display is adjusted according to the time zone preference on the user profile for authenticated users. For anonymous users the time is adjusted to the Server Preferred Time Zone.</p>